  i  rise to  support the  election  laws amendment  bill 2016   i  would  like  to  bring  to  the  notice of  the  minister  that though  the  ap  reorganization  act  which  was  passed  in  2014  we  are  yet  to get the necessary amendments to go through the delimitation exercise in both andhra pradesh  and  telangana    it  requires  a  constitution  amendment  for  that  or  an amendment  to  the  ap  reorganization  act    so  i  beseech  the  government  to please  consider  this  and  to  do  it  at  the  earliest    i  would  like  to  also  bring  to  the notice of the house that nonresident indians who retain their indian citizenship around the world are not given this right to vote  so i would like to urge upon the government to consider giving voting rights to nris  